🚀 STEP 0 — CREATE PROJECT
1. Open VS Code
2. Create folder:
employee-api
3. Open folder in VS Code
4. Open terminal:
Ctrl + `
5. Initialize project:
npm init -y
6. Install packages (as per instructions PDF):
npm install express body-parser mongoose joi
📁 STEP 1 — CREATE FILES (VERY IMPORTANT)

Inside folder create EXACTLY these files:

server.js
db.js
routes.js
validation.js
✍️ STEP 2 — WRITE CODE (FILE BY FILE)

STEP 3 — RUN PROJECT
node server.js

👉 Output:

MongoDB Connected
